#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.hsplit.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.hsplit"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:1 of
msgid "Split a tensor into multiple sub-tensors horizontally (column-wise)."
msgstr "将一个张量水平（按列）分割成多个子张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:3 of
msgid ""
"Please refer to the `split` documentation.  `hsplit` is equivalent to "
"`split` with ``axis=1``, the tensor is always split along the second axis"
" regardless of the tensor dimension."
msgstr ""
"请参阅 `split` 文档。`hsplit` 等价于 ``axis=1`` 的 `split`，张量总是沿"
"第二个轴进行分割，无论张量的维度如何。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:9 of
msgid ":py:obj:`split`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:10 of
msgid "Split an array into multiple sub-arrays of equal size."
msgstr "将一个数组分割成多个大小相等的子数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:13 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.hsplit.hsplit:42 of
msgid "With a higher dimensional array the split is still along the second axis."
msgstr "对于更高维度的数组，分割仍然沿着第二个轴进行。"

